summary: Sometimes life can be hard. Sometimes deep thoughts come into my head that shouldn’t be here. Sometimes I feel like the world...
body:
Sometimes life can be hard. Sometimes deep thoughts come into my head that shouldn’t be here. Sometimes I feel like the world hates me. I wanna Yell and scream my pain, my thoughts, stuff I wanna say but I feel ashamed for saying it out loud because of peers around me who make me feel like that. I wish we could just all be happy and kind.


But then that’s called life. We will always have our ups and downs and somehow we gotta find a way to push through it and not give up even though we may think it’s the right choice. I’m telling you it’s not.


Lilan has helped me through so many things in my life. She is so kind and sweet and her heart for her fans is like the biggest heart I’ve ever seen. Thank you Lilan for literally everything. She makes me and so many others happy and we need a person like Lilan. I wish we could all have a lilan because life would be so much happier😂


Anyways, sorry for a sappy post. I try to stay positive on the internet, but I think sharing how you feel is good. I can’t keep bottling up my feelings and thoughts anymore.


If you ever need anyone to talk too, I’m here:) message me!! My messages are always open;)


Reblog this if you agree with what I said, or even make your own post. Some people just need to talk to someone who can sit and listen to them. 💞 we all need that.

summary: I bet you’ve been asked this so many times but... what are your hopes for Season 3 of AM? Anything in general
question: I bet you’ve been asked this so many times but... what are your hopes for Season 3 of AM? Anything in general
answer:
In general, I just want all the characters to be happy and get the ending they deserve.

Assuming S3 is the last season, this is what I want for the characters:

For Andi, I want her to get the family she always wanted with her parents getting back together and maybe a sister/brother to add to the family? I also want her to finally know where she and Jonah stand in their relationship bc this whole “will they? won’t they” has been exhausted too many times already and she deserves better than that.

For Cyrus, I want him to gain a whole new set of self-confidence and be the one to confess his feelings to TJ first because that will show how far he’s come since S1 and TJ was a really big help in his gaining self-confidence anyway. He deserves his happy ending with the boyfriend he always wanted and I want him to come out to Jonah and his family, or at least his 4 shrink parents and know how much he’s loved. I think that would make his whole storyline come to full circle.

For Buffy, I want her to be with the one who truly gets her (Marty) and continue to make change with her starting a girls’ basketball team at their school. It’ll also be nice to see more of her friendship with TJ and her support of his’ and Cyrus’ relationship. I also would like for the audience to meet her dad bc she mentions she has one but we’ve never seen him.

For Jonah, I think it goes without saying that I want him to tell Andi about his panic attacks/that he suffers from anxiety and seek professional help for it. Same as I said for Andi, I want them to stop the whole “will they? won’t they” with Jandi. I also want us to get background information on his family and dig deeper on his past and for him to find out Cyrus is gay and support him. And I must add I want him to become friends with TJ and Marty bc that’s an iconic trio and I’m still curious how TJ and Jonah know each other…

And I must add I want him to become friends with TJ and Marty bc that’s an iconic trio and I’m still curious how TJ and Jonah know each other…
